            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3950.0118357297765!2d-79.0612349!3d-8.100274299999999!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x91ad3db464fe96a9%3A0xc58f067710ea469d!2sBr%C3%BCning%20School!5e0!3m2!1ses!2spe!4v1769692220299!5m2!1ses!2spe" 
