            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              Cerca de principales avenidas y con acceso a transporte público
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 text-center">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-colegio-yellow rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-colegio-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-colegio-blue mb-2">Agendar Visita</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              Programa una cita y conoce nuestras instalaciones personalmente
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 text-center">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-colegio-blue rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
